title: This seems to be disappearing in retail settings.
description:
For some reason this full-synthetic 20W50 oil is becoming a scarce commodity. I have a vintage Volkswagen that runs so much cooler with this oil over the HD30 that is also disappearing from retail shelves.
I also use it in my small air-cooled engines on my lawnmowers. The price was competitive and I received it in two days. I would recommend this to anyone for their motorcycle or any of the other applications I mentioned.
date: Reviewed in the United States on July 19, 2023
